<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Autonomous Bot Maze Runner</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #1e272e;
